This page lists modes for Emacs which are designed primarily for managing references and bibliographical data:

=== Major Modes ===
* [[BibTeX]] -- a major mode for editing and validating BibTeX files.
* [[EbibMode]] -- a major mode for managing BibTeX databases.
* [[Bibus]] -- a major mode for displaying and managing reference keys.

=== Minor Modes ===
* [[RefdbMode]] -- a minor mode which provides access to [http://refdb.sourceforge.net/|RefDB].
* [[RefTeX]] -- a minor mode which provides support for creating labels, references and citations in LaTeX.

=== Discussion ===
